Busia Governor Sospeter Ojaamong has defended Deputy Governor Kizito Wangalwa&rsquo;s remarks at a burial last week.Wangalwa told residents to re-elect him and Ojaamong because &ldquo;the Teso community deserves to hold the governor&rsquo;s position for two terms.&rdquo; On Tuesday, Ojaamong said there is nothing wrong with asking residents to re-elect them. He called for unity.